caption.text:
If you think about it...
Life is like music, and music is like life. In life there are sad/hurtful memories, fun moments, hopeful times and some weird things along the way. In music there are sad ballads, swing, gospel, funk, etc.
And if I am to tell you the best way to enjoy these different types of music, it is to just groove along üë¶.
Groove during the happy moments when it's time for us to swing and dance, groove when we feel hopeful and grateful for God's blessings, and also groove during the inevitable times of sorrow and hardship.
So friends, no matter what type of song your life is playing for you, ALWAYS be grooving. It is just another song in your life album! 
Am I making any sense tho?
